OL,3,CCalls for 12 weeks' fully paid
OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,FMothers in Jersey could soon have
OL,7,Faccess to 12 weeks of paid maternity
OL,8,Fleave at their full salary, if
OL,9,Frecommendations from the island's
OL,10,FFamily-Friendly Legislation Scrutiny
OL,11,FPanel are adopted.
OL,13,FProposed changes also include the
OL,14,Fintroduction of measures specifically
OL,15,Fsupporting single-parent households,
OL,16,Fand the extension of parental leave
OL,17,Fentitlements to grandparents and close
OL,18,Ffamily members.
