OL,3,CCalls for 12 weeks' fully paid
OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,FIt comes after a year-long
OL,7,Finvestigation into the impact of the
OL,8,Fisland's Employment Laws, which found
OL,9,Fthat not all types of families have
OL,10,Fequal access to the benefits designed
OL,11,Fto support them and enhance early-
OL,12,Fyears development.
OL,14,FDeputy Louise Doublet, the Panel's
OL,15,FChair, says their report highlights
OL,16,Fsome of the reasons why the island's
OL,17,Fbirthrate is falling and many young
OL,18,Ffamilies are now looking to leave.
