OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,F"Families are in crisis", she
OL,7,Fexplains, "many families are really
OL,8,Fstruggling - and we need to improve
OL,9,Fsupport for families and businesses as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible."
OL,12,FSome of their key findings include:
OL,14,FDeputy Doublet says she thinks "the
OL,15,Fstruggles of single parents have been
OL,16,Flargely invisible until now".
