OL,3,CCalls for 12 weeks' fully paid
OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,FThe Panel's report explains that these
OL,7,Fchanges are necessary to ensure that
OL,8,Frights are "accessible, equitable,
OL,9,Fclearly communicated, financially
OL,10,Ffeasible, and aligned with the
OL,11,Frealities of modern family life".
OL,13,FIt is already a legal requirement for
OL,14,Femployers to provide six weeks of
OL,15,Fmaternity leave on full pay, but
OL,16,FDeputy Doublet says the additional six
OL,17,Fweeks of state-funded leave on a
OL,18,Fperson's regular salary would change
OL,19,Flives.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
