OL,3,CCalls for 12 weeks' fully paid
OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,FHer Panel's research found that 12
OL,7,Fweeks of parental leave is linked to
OL,8,Fdecreased psychological distress,
OL,9,Flower infant mortality, and better
OL,10,Fattachment.
OL,12,F"All mothers should be entitled to
OL,13,Fspend that time with their babies and
OL,14,Fwhat we found was across the board was
OL,15,Ffamilies of all different income
OL,16,Flevels are struggling", she explains.
OL,18,F"The money would either have to come
OL,19,Ffrom making savings in other areas, or
OL,20,Fwe might have to look at taxation",
OL,21,Fshe adds.
