OL,4,Cmaternity cover and 'grandparent leave'
OL,6,F"We do need to have these difficult
OL,7,Fconversations about how much of our
OL,8,Ftaxes we are putting towards
OL,9,Fsupporting families, because
OL,10,Fultimately families are leaving the
OL,11,Fisland and people aren't starting
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,14,F"If we don't have families in the
OL,15,Fisland then we won't have the tax take
OL,16,Fto support our public services."
