OL,6,FSharon Ralston, owner of Hair Central
OL,7,Fhairdressing salon in St Helier, says
OL,8,Fif the Government are looking to
OL,9,Fextend parental leave, it is essential
OL,10,Fthey pick up the bill too.
OL,12,F"That has a huge impact because our
OL,13,Fcash reserves are not huge and we are
OL,14,Fa service-based industry - so those
OL,15,Fstylists that are then off are not
OL,16,Fcontributing to the business, and the
OL,17,Fclients going to other stylists are
OL,18,Fcontributing to their wage", she
OL,19,Fexplains.
