OL,6,F"We've got to find those extra cash
OL,7,Freserves to pay (maternity cover),
OL,8,Fwhich can be quite tough in this
OL,9,Fclimate."
OL,11,FIn response, Social Security Minister,
OL,12,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, says she is
OL,13,F"grateful for the thorough and
OL,14,Fdetailed report on the Family Friendly
OL,15,FLegislation review.
OL,17,F"Given the number and complexity of
OL,18,Fthe recommendations, each will be
OL,19,Freviewed in detail, and a
OL,20,Fcomprehensive response will be
OL,21,Fprovided in the required timeframe."
